    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/30/35428890/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_8034107497636060192.png",
                "id": "talent26325",
                "key": "Wolflord's Strike",
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Wolflord's Strike"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>, attaches 2 stacks of <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Golden Corrosion</span> to target character, and summons <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Rifthound Skull</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Golden Corrosion</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> If the character to which this is attached is on standby, then that character will take 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> for every <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span> that this effect has.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 1</span> (Can stack. Max 3 stacks.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/30/35428890/88bee9c24128a7b8fae306dd5feecea3_2679251013071239564.png",
                "id": "talent9391",
                "key": "Howling Riftcall ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Howling Riftcall "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>, deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> to all opposing characters on standby, then attaches <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Golden Corrosion</span> to all opposing characters.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Golden Corrosion</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> If the character to which this is attached is on standby, then that character will take 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> for every <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span> that this effect has.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 1</span> (Can stack. Max 3 stacks.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/30/35428890/54fafafd3720e95ffa305f16d15dbfca_9132865679559900776.png",
                "id": "talent22865",
                "key": "Golden Cankerbind ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Golden Cankerbind "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>. Attach <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Golden Corrosion</span> to target character.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/30/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_4387145866698679982.png",
                "id": "talent93738",
                "key": "Rifthound Skull",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [
                  {
                    "description": "",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/30/35428890/9d1b4f3533ead11a0ba9d42b0eecf56e_5415691449280088565.png"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "Rifthound Skull"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Reacts with Elements if they are already applied:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/30/35428890/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_7768812597331414069.png",
                "id": "talent51974",
                "key": "Geo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Geo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Piercing DMG</span></strong><br>Piercing DMG cannot be increased by any bonuses, but cannot be defended against using Shields or DMG Immunity either.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/30/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_8873877384169421359.png",
                "id": "talent46081",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
